WEBVTT

31:45.490 --> 31:46.460 line:80%
Mrs. Zhuang.

31:46.460 --> 31:48.250 line:80%
Here's some homemade puffed rice candy—

31:48.250 --> 31:49.910 line:80%
a little snack for Changning.

31:50.810 --> 31:51.480 line:80%
But...

31:51.620 --> 31:52.290 line:80%
Take it.

31:52.290 --> 31:55.220 line:80%
Changyu, I heard your husband
was writing Spring Festival couplets for people.

31:55.220 --> 31:57.810 line:80%
Our family hasn't gotten ours written yet,
either,
